<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xuān jiào de duì wǔ yào cóng zhè lǐ chū fā 迦南1267</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de huà jiù xiàng nà dōng rì de yáng guāng yòu hǎo xiàng shā mò liú tǎng de gān quán
 shèng líng de huǒ yàn yǐ jīng diǎn rán yì guó de tǔ de zǎo yǐ sōng ruǎn
 yǒng bù fàng qì shì wǒ men de xìn niàn tuó líng shēng shēng xiǎng zài ěr biān
 xuān jiào de duì wǔ yào cóng zhè lǐ chū fā shén de zhǐ yì hé shí jiān bù huì gǎi biàn</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1267</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>